og/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca50e90b8cf479a17ad2a2cf9ba7dfb8d62015e","tid":1494484,"uid":41420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804aaf6f8cda911d3e8bb0c8d7c0fc1518a21a0e","tid":1494484,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:21:20.000Z","msg":"要keep住問<br />\n<br />\n一次無問兩次無問<br />\n<br />\n三四次就變約定俗成<br />\n<br />\n雖然可能問完都答唔到啲咩<br />\n<br />\n但都要keep住問<br />\n<br />\n除左記者 市民都要問"},{"pid":"5fb2b38cc39d38c3aa18cbdc5c15ef7fb11d8bba","tid":1494484,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:29:41.000Z","msg":"支那匪扮警察，又唔熟本洪法例呢？"},{"pid":"dff0e5935b28b57ab8dd7db42361b78cb45a12ee","tid":1494484,"uid":41420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:32:25.000Z","msg":"如果佢話訓練制服無，就問佢點解兩個月都著訓練制服<br />\n如果佢話件制服無位放no. 就show 相同片俾佢睇曾經有放到no. 既制服<br />\n如果佢話警察執勤唔需要帶委任証或者咩現場有一個警察証明全部都係警察，就讀警察通例叫佢解<br />\n如果佢叫你去投訴警察科，最好就print 定d 相指明要投訴邊個警察叫佢提供姓名編號，今日無就聽日俾，問到有為止<br />\n如果佢話無資料，就日日keep 住問問到有資料為止<br />\n總之唔可以俾班狗甚至大眾丟淡件事"},{"pid":"81d84eeef314e93d2c4a3f7f61644c4b6dd9c566","tid":1494484,"uid":287410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:37:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3774366ef2b54a666386061a7834622f06064335","tid":1494484,"uid":41420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:13:12.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"1be930c69e375a03e3b1b394736ec8e8a9b43f2e","tid":1494484,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4878c96ea5b7a8d298217cf0058b079432e03e8","tid":1494484,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":